pid":"38837b23ef4493207bf362b5b83866ab0f3b5e90","tid":363820,"uid":5802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"佢聽係一回事<br />\n廚房點做又係另一回事"},{"pid":"1c0d7a06560301af512d4195abc679d71769e286","tid":363820,"uid":31834,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"DLS... 又係俾少少錢以為自己係大爺，係食家... 得啖笑..."},{"pid":"34987f5863674b1e9f4f0c73b98fccdfd47cbb28","tid":363820,"uid":137981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"叫温泉蛋啦， 仲脆咩邊"},{"pid":"45911e52f781f76b909b71fb321edfb994a87da1","tid":363820,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:59:40.000Z","msg":"脆邊都做唔到，垃圾餐廳執左佢啦<br />\n<br />\n依家啲廚房佬識洗碗就做到"},{"pid":"0d488f1366c15fc9d3d34401c86af38447b5da2c","tid":363820,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T03:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>麻撚煩</blockquote><br />\n食個茶記大X樂最多依啲傻鳩<br />\n<del>食薯條又走鹽</del><br />\n飲杯凍檸茶又少甜少冰<br />\n咁你索性咪撚飲/食算啦</blockquote><br />\n薯條走鹽係迫佢用新炸起果托批，你識條鐵咩<br />\n識人要人走鹽再比多包鹽</blockquote><br />\n咁你岩喎<br />\n我del依句</blockquote><br />\n薯條新炸起要rest一陣先正<br />\n新炸起成口油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee42cf7ec945d47ef49bad5c458b46e5c9ba67b","tid":363820,"uid":125665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>麻撚煩</blockquote><br />\n食個茶記大X樂最多依啲傻鳩<br />\n食薯條又走鹽<br />\n飲杯凍檸茶又少甜少冰<br />\n咁你索性咪撚飲/食算啦</blockquote><br />\n少甜少冰都要比你屌 依家免費定好撚平呀?</blockquote><br />\n宜家出面d野飲落咁多冰 杯野飲幾啖都無喇 叫少冰咪唔洗比你搵笨囉 同埋少甜有咩問題 唔係叫你糖水另上已經算好喇</blockquote><br />\n杯野係熱架靠冰整凍佢<br />\n少冰杯野點會凍</blockquote><br />\nD冰直情係過多 叫少冰先係正常份量都會夠凍同埋咁多冰又令到杯野淡晒  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825c8830a9d12cc7b328adb8acb8b62c07c732f6","tid":363820,"uid":70605,"like":21,"dislike":0,"